import React, {useState} from 'react'; import './style.css' import Repost from './chat.png'; import wse from './heart.png'; import chtoto from './exchange.png' import tweet from './twitter.png' export const Tweet = ({name, text, retweet, comments, likes, time, isLiked}) => { const [liked, setLiked] = useState(isLiked) return (
{name}
{time}
{text}
{retweet}
{comments}
{likes}
) }
